snippet: Jeff Demps, a former Florida running back and a silver medalist in the 4x100 relay in the London Olympics, has signed with the New England Patriots, the team announced on Friday.
abstract: NFL Roundup; New England Patriots sign Olympic medalist Jeff Demps; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Jeff Demps, a former Florida running back and a silver medalist in the 4x100 relay in the London Olympics, has signed with the New England Patriots, the team announced on Friday.

headline.seo: Demps, Olympic Medalist, Reaches Terms With Patriots
headline.main: Olympian and Patriots Reach Terms on a Deal
headline.print_headline: Olympian And Patriots Reach Terms On a Deal
